4 types of access Modifiers in Apex

=> global - It is used globally within or outside the namespace (Used in class , method, variable) , scope - all
=> pubic -  It is visible to the classes which are in the same nameSpace (Used in class , method, variable) , scope - all
=> protected - only visible to the class which extends & inner Classes. scope - variables , methods
=> private - visible only within the class 
